My name is Bill Manahan. Jerry Koops, who is the owner
 
of Portside Marina in Port Stanley,ON, Canada has asked me to contact you 

on his behalf as he is not internet savy. In 2005, a then partner of  
Jerry's , David Taylor, had a then boater at the marina, Paul Nichols,
post  
information on Blogger concerning Portside Marina.
Mr Koops has always been the owner of Portside Marina and Mr Taylor was a 

minority partner. That partnership has since dissolved and , in fact, the 

posting in question was never agreed to by Mr Koops.
The information contained in the blog with relation to Portside Marina is 

inaccurate ans is causing Mr. Koops some concern.
The poster, Paul Nichols, is no longer in the country and cannot be  
contacted.
Mr. Koops is requesting that this blog be removed from the site.
Pleaser advise me on this matter either via email at  
grampianbill@hotmail.com or by phone at 519-868-8844.
